urdu transliteration text:
Yeh khat mei shah ne likha habib aajaoTumhaara dost hai tanha habib aajao
Your friend is alone, Habib please come
@HujjatELC

Shaheed kaise huwa woh bataawoge aakar, tum haale muslim e bekas sunaawoge aakar, ruqaiyya takti hai rasta, habib aajao
Ruqayya is waiting for you eagerly, Habib please come
@HujjatELC

Mujhe hai yaad woh lamha jo rab ki marzi se, tum hoke zinda meri baat sun ne aaye the, bula raha hoo(n) dobara, habib aajao
I am calling you once again, Habib please come
@HujjatELC

Dare batool dobara jalaaya jaayega, tumhaare dost pe khanjar chalaaya jaayega, nahi hai waqt ziyaada, habib aajao
there is not much time left, Habib please come
@HujjatELC

Yeh khat nahi isse behno ki aarzo samjo, hamaare lafzo ko zainab ki guftagu samjo, behen yeh kehti hai bhaiyya, habib aajao
your sister says, brother Habib please come
@HujjatELC

Behen ne usko "Takallum" jo bhaayi samja tha, pukaari shaame ghareeba(n) mei saaniye zahra, hamaara lut ta hai parda, habib aajao
